citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on 31-May-
2022. The inspector spoke with a member of the household who stated that no one was available for the inspection. The
inspector then left the facility.
End Section
